00:42:08.299 --> 00:42:09.659
in the state of Washington

00:42:09.659 --> 00:42:12.939
that was arrested for preaching on the corner.

00:42:12.939 --> 00:42:14.979
And I thought, oh my.

00:42:14.979 --> 00:42:16.699
I just said a couple hours ago

00:42:16.739 --> 00:42:19.099
that we live in a nation where we can do that.

00:42:20.539 --> 00:42:23.059
It's changing, it's changing.

00:42:25.179 --> 00:42:27.219
But God has not changed.

00:42:27.219 --> 00:42:31.859
He's the same yesterday and today and forever.

00:42:31.859 --> 00:42:34.019
Listen, your circumstances might change,

00:42:34.019 --> 00:42:35.499
but God doesn't change.

00:42:35.499 --> 00:42:37.199
You make a commitment to obey God

00:42:37.199 --> 00:42:39.779
in the area of your finances.

00:42:39.779 --> 00:42:42.819
You expect that there's going to be some unexpected bills.

00:42:43.899 --> 00:42:44.919
Right?

00:42:44.919 --> 00:42:45.759
Why?

00:42:45.759 --> 00:42:48.159
Because Satan wants to find out if you're serious.

00:42:49.639 --> 00:42:50.679
Oh, you're going to obey God?

